title: Add Reference to a Org Roam Node
tags: @zettel doomemacs orgroam _method
roam-id: 516d1e27-3abd-4fc9-aa44-a84b83434cb8
roam-refs: https://jethrokuan.github.io/org-roam-guide/
type: text/markdown

- while you're inside the node press `SPC m m o r`
- a new Ref: popup will appear
- you can insert the video url or book url inside
- then your node will contain a new property as "ROAM<sub>REFS</sub>"
- you can also add more refs into this list
